  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The 18F-FDOPA PET tracer is an amino acid analogue that can be used to visualize high-grade
      glioma not clearly identified on diagnostic MRI. Use of 18F-FDOPA PET will permit
      neurosurgeons to achieve a complete resection more frequently.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
